{"tid":1021593,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[推廣有圖]打厭左廣東牌？試下打考腦既港式台灣牌！","createTime":"2019-02-14T10:51:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T11:23:33.000Z","uid":201169,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"72286528b0cabe3ed59ba396e1cd4753e05ea115","tid":1021593,"uid":201169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:51:43.000Z","msg":"打廣東牌2家著一條底褲？又留局？<br />\n打跑馬仔？又包槓？又唔中碼？<br />\n不如試下港式台灣牌啦！<br />\n邊個發明我就唔知啦，但係勝在節奏快同用腦，講技術，唔喺下下靠運氣！<br />\n<br />\n事先聲明，我唔喺專家，亦唔喺想推廣賭博。只喺希望鐘意打或者有興趣學打既人可以交流下！港式台灣牌既特色就係家家都有唔同既打法，千變萬化，所以打之前一定要講好點打。我組合左幾個網同自己親身打過既經驗，做左個總結俾大家參考下。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vke4rEx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvke4rEx.png&h=e2fa9b86&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SeWeOST.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSeWeOST.png&h=fcf76e96&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sBNYv6e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsBNYv6e.png&h=872a6baf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本上玩法就係鬥快食糊，狂拉，唔喺下下都要食大牌既。有時一開牌好似好爛，樣樣齊又9唔搭8，不過用下腦都可以砌到副大牌出黎架！<br />\n<br />\n有咩問題即管問，答到盡力答！"},{"pid":"afc16fa1ded8649dd7306dbb88073ee45632be51","tid":1021593,"uid":154872,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:53:17.000Z","msg":"我地呢鋪打ge係美國牌<br />\n<br />\n可以互相交換三隻牌<br />\n<br />\n莊家有權交換多一次"},{"pid":"c2d26203c898367a54c47ef7f4c629bea3db8678","tid":1021593,"uid":175125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:56:56.000Z","msg":"唔打花應該幾好<br />\n打花不了"},{"pid":"552ef57bfc257967c01e9355eb5888fed5d89907","tid":1021593,"uid":79145,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T11:06:18.000Z","msg":"食完糊要查字典咁先計到幾多番，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75fb227cf5665f92fac4dca855fda5519ec76dc3","tid":1021593,"uid":34698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T11:06:56.000Z","msg":"打日麻啦"},{"pid":"69a94f459c0a069030fa9b8ff647a87540cdcdb4","tid":1021593,"uid":17405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afc16fa1ded8649dd7306dbb88073ee45632be51","tid":1021593,"uid":154872,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:53:17.000Z","msg":"我地呢鋪打ge係美國牌<br />\n<br />\n可以互相交換三隻牌<br />\n<br />\n莊家有權交換多一次"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T11:07:30.000Z","msg":"做莊未必好"},{"pid":"17a85bada872cbc3dc6a5fae6ba13edf875e261f","tid":1021593,"uid":6619,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T11:23:33.000Z","msg":"要用腦就打日麻"}]}